## 1、手动扩缩容机制

### 使用示例

#### nginx-deployment.yaml

```
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: nginx-deployment
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: nginx
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: nginx
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: nginx
        image: docker.m.daocloud.io/nginx:1.28.3
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
```

